author: Dr. Delaram J. Taghipour
title: Why coronavirus can make some severely ill and others hardly at all
description: New data reveals dramatically stark sex disparities.
content:
COVID-19 does not impact us all the same. In fact, a growing body of evidence finds that the virus seems to hit men harder than women.
Early in the epidemic, researchers' best guess was that the difference could be chalked up to higher rates of smoking among… [+7136 chars]
